title: Brookstone Store Locations 12.2007
name: Brookstone Store Locations 12.2007
description:
Brookstone is a chain of retail stores in the United States. Brookstone first opened in 1973 in Peterborough, New Hampshire and is now headquarterd in Merrimack, New Hampshire. They sell many products ranging from radar detectors to massage chairs. 

This dataset displays all of the Brookstone locations across the United States. The dataset contains the store's full physical address, phone, and lat/lon coordinates. Addresses were obtained from brookstone.com and are current as of 12.2007. Addresses were geocoded to obtain their lat/lon coordinates.

For more information, go to brookstone.com

Data accessed on December 18, 2007
